{"tid":937241,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)獵血都市 怪形 顫慄異次元","createTime":"2018-12-11T11:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T19:36:43.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8371c080c8e80bb6ec194372798b1e1c9e4e88e5","tid":937241,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:40:41.000Z","msg":"]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=5%2Fc7HLhlv3LDDXG6ZXhyqv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=bff8f972\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=5%2Fc7HLhlv3LDDXG6ZXhyqv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=29c7b4eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=5%2Fc7HLhlv3LDDXG6ZXhyqv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=44fcaf76\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b4/Daybreakers_ver2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb4%2FDaybreakers_ver2.jpg&h=47c0778f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c1/ThingPoster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc1%2FThingPoster.jpg&h=bdca2bc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/3d/Pandorum-Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F3d%2FPandorum-Poster.jpg&h=a3bcdf0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.世界成了吸血鬼的天下，由於人類越來越少，吸血鬼急需研究出血液的替代品，血液專家愛德華&middot;道爾頓（伊森&middot;霍克飾）從事這項工作，其老闆查爾斯&middot;布羅姆利（薩姆&middot;尼爾飾）是一位野心家，他希望通過壟斷新的替代品獲得巨額利潤<br />\n<br />\n2.一日，兩名挪威人駕駛一架直昇機，在南極洲的凍土地帶上瘋狂追殺一隻雪橇犬，這隻狗好不容易逃進了美國科學家的研究站中，其中一名挪威人因錯誤被手榴弾炸死、另一名挪威人因固執地追殺那頭雪橇犬時，同時誤傷一位美國基地隊員，結果被迫遭到美國基地隊長防衛射殺，令此事成為懸案<br />\n<br />\n3.近兩百年後地球人口爆炸，滿載人類希望，冷凍睡眠航向外太空的新樂土。隨著船艙裡航員紛紛甦醒，從深度睡眠而凌亂斷裂的記憶，逐漸拼湊自己的身分和此航的目的，同時不明攻擊事件讓他們發現，船上似乎有著意料外的東西.......<br />\n<br />\n9 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=5%2Fc7HLhlv3LDDXG6ZXhyqv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=5a29b47e\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=5%2Fc7HLhlv3LDDXG6ZXhyqv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ec10cec3\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8142fee2a2bb68b62b9c3c163acb6677fad98e0","tid":937241,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/big